  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Objective:</u></strong></h2>In UNCLE Z, you and up to six brave survivors have the crucial task of caring for your uncle, who has been infected by the terrible zombie plague. Time is against you as you desperately search for clues that will lead to your long-awaited rescue. But be careful, every step you take could be your last!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Key Mechanics:</u></strong></h2><strong>Resource Management:</strong> <br>The game offers an immersive and challenging experience, where the scarcity of resources is just the beginning of your problems. Hunger and thirst are constant threats, requiring you and your team to make quick, smart decisions to survive another day.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/c8aa73425e106405a18a2de9b6454f9c.poster.avif?t=1734023093\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/c8aa73425e106405a18a2de9b6454f9c.webm?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/c8aa73425e106405a18a2de9b6454f9c.mp4?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Resolve Chaos:</strong> <br>Keeping your base running is essential for survival amid the chaos of the zombie apocalypse. Daily tasks include searching for vital resources such as food, water and building materials, while you and your team face constant zombie attacks and your uncle doesn't seem to be much help...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/8e45836beeaf605bab4b9885101d5ddc.poster.avif?t=1734023093\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/8e45836beeaf605bab4b9885101d5ddc.webm?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/8e45836beeaf605bab4b9885101d5ddc.mp4?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Keep the House Clean:</strong><br>The infected blood spread across the floor of the house poses a constant threat, as any inadvertent contact could result in infection and transformation into a zombie. Keeping the area clean and taking extra precautions when handling contaminated waste are essential measures to prevent the spread of infection and ensure the safety of all team members.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/9a089a472c0c13e79c26536c4dd9eac3.poster.avif?t=1734023093\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/9a089a472c0c13e79c26536c4dd9eac3.webm?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/9a089a472c0c13e79c26536c4dd9eac3.mp4?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Keep the House Secure:</strong><br>It is crucial to fortify your defenses, repair structural damage, and ensure all systems such as power and communications are operational. Every detail counts in the fight for survival, and the ability to keep your base functioning amidst the chaos will determine your fate in this unforgiving world.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/e0718cbdc331e9a4312d8714a805cc4a.poster.avif?t=1734023093\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/e0718cbdc331e9a4312d8714a805cc4a.webm?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/e0718cbdc331e9a4312d8714a805cc4a.mp4?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Stay Alert:</strong> <br>Be alert on expeditions to not be left behind.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/77ed9b7a8d5d4cac63dfc567ce1e0422.poster.avif?t=1734023093\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/77ed9b7a8d5d4cac63dfc567ce1e0422.webm?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/77ed9b7a8d5d4cac63dfc567ce1e0422.mp4?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Combat:</strong> <br>Combat strategy is the key to defeating the hordes of zombies that roam the post-apocalyptic world. Players need to be constantly alert and prepared to face these relentless and differentiated enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/93aac09f5d27fcb6ef6a14222ad232cf.poster.avif?t=1734023093\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/93aac09f5d27fcb6ef6a14222ad232cf.webm?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/93aac09f5d27fcb6ef6a14222ad232cf.mp4?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Find Resources:</strong> <br>Expeditions are a vital part of the survival strategy. Players can organize exploration teams to venture outside the safety of their base in search of essential resources and clues to rescue.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/de6148b3138ba963df989f78945eaa27.poster.avif?t=1734023093\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/de6148b3138ba963df989f78945eaa27.webm?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/de6148b3138ba963df989f78945eaa27.mp4?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Diseases:</strong> <br>Avoid catching diseases and always have some medicine to treat them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/748ddf35f0377611330e436cb306f9d9.poster.avif?t=1734023093\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/748ddf35f0377611330e436cb306f9d9.webm?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/748ddf35f0377611330e436cb306f9d9.mp4?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Exploration:</strong> <br>Explore locations in search of weapons, resources and a way to escape to safety.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/63c6c459330c3c4c99a03f3e4fa07324.poster.avif?t=1734023093\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/63c6c459330c3c4c99a03f3e4fa07324.webm?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/63c6c459330c3c4c99a03f3e4fa07324.mp4?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Crafting:</strong><br>The importance of using resources effectively and in concert cannot be underestimated. Each item, from food and water to building materials and ammunition, plays a crucial role in players' survival and maintaining their base.<br><br>Do you have what it takes to face the chaos and emerge as a hero? Join us at UNCLE Z and find out!",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Objective:</u></strong></h2>In UNCLE Z, you and up to six brave survivors have the crucial task of caring for your uncle, who has been infected by the terrible zombie plague. Time is against you as you desperately search for clues that will lead to your long-awaited rescue. But be careful, every step you take could be your last!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Key Mechanics:</u></strong></h2><strong>Resource Management:</strong> <br>The game offers an immersive and challenging experience, where the scarcity of resources is just the beginning of your problems. Hunger and thirst are constant threats, requiring you and your team to make quick, smart decisions to survive another day.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/c8aa73425e106405a18a2de9b6454f9c.poster.avif?t=1734023093\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/c8aa73425e106405a18a2de9b6454f9c.webm?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/c8aa73425e106405a18a2de9b6454f9c.mp4?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Resolve Chaos:</strong> <br>Keeping your base running is essential for survival amid the chaos of the zombie apocalypse. Daily tasks include searching for vital resources such as food, water and building materials, while you and your team face constant zombie attacks and your uncle doesn't seem to be much help...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/8e45836beeaf605bab4b9885101d5ddc.poster.avif?t=1734023093\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steam