ai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/e0718cbdc331e9a4312d8714a805cc4a.webm?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/e0718cbdc331e9a4312d8714a805cc4a.mp4?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Stay Alert:</strong> <br>Be alert on expeditions to not be left behind.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/77ed9b7a8d5d4cac63dfc567ce1e0422.poster.avif?t=1734023093\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/77ed9b7a8d5d4cac63dfc567ce1e0422.webm?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/77ed9b7a8d5d4cac63dfc567ce1e0422.mp4?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Combat:</strong> <br>Combat strategy is the key to defeating the hordes of zombies that roam the post-apocalyptic world. Players need to be constantly alert and prepared to face these relentless and differentiated enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/93aac09f5d27fcb6ef6a14222ad232cf.poster.avif?t=1734023093\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/93aac09f5d27fcb6ef6a14222ad232cf.webm?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/93aac09f5d27fcb6ef6a14222ad232cf.mp4?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Find Resources:</strong> <br>Expeditions are a vital part of the survival strategy. Players can organize exploration teams to venture outside the safety of their base in search of essential resources and clues to rescue.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/de6148b3138ba963df989f78945eaa27.poster.avif?t=1734023093\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/de6148b3138ba963df989f78945eaa27.webm?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/de6148b3138ba963df989f78945eaa27.mp4?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Diseases:</strong> <br>Avoid catching diseases and always have some medicine to treat them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/748ddf35f0377611330e436cb306f9d9.poster.avif?t=1734023093\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/748ddf35f0377611330e436cb306f9d9.webm?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/748ddf35f0377611330e436cb306f9d9.mp4?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Exploration:</strong> <br>Explore locations in search of weapons, resources and a way to escape to safety.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/63c6c459330c3c4c99a03f3e4fa07324.poster.avif?t=1734023093\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/63c6c459330c3c4c99a03f3e4fa07324.webm?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2815690/extras/63c6c459330c3c4c99a03f3e4fa07324.mp4?t=1734023093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Crafting:</strong><br>The importance of using resources effectively and in concert cannot be underestimated. Each item, from food and water to building materials and ammunition, plays a crucial role in players' survival and maintaining their base.<br><br>Do you have what it takes to face the chaos and emerge as a hero? Join us at UNCLE Z and find out!",
